items.name: var CFByteOrderLittleEndian: __CFByteOrder
items.desc: Multi-byte values are stored with the least-significant bytes stored first. Pentium CPUs are little endian.

items.name: var CFByteOrderBigEndian: __CFByteOrder
items.desc: Multi-byte values are stored with the most-significant bytes stored first. PowerPC CPUs are big endian.
